node.text: It’s scary and incredible at the same time 😮🔥🔥🔥
this video almost gave me a heart attack
@mickeykpics  Yep and I had it muted and oh my god it was MORE majestic and thrilling without that music! Much better muted.
Maybe skip the dramatic music bext time?
@afra.99k The day hasn’t been wasted….I learned something new. 😂
Can Tiger Sharks be larger than Great White Sharks? This one appears massive.
That move was just to intimidate
Like don't you dare fuck wit me bro 🤨
Damn, that second bite was a threat 💀💀💀
